---
title: Gobble Up Turkey Stir-Fry with Coconut Rice
description: Many people forget about turkey except at Christmas, which is a shame as it's lean and flavourful and great in all sorts of dishes. Today we're making a colourful Asian stir-fry with a surprising secret ingredient: ketchup! It  rings a delicious sweet and sour note and is actually used by lots of Chinese restaurant chefs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gobble-up-turkey-stir-fry-ad5c6170-81d2e54a.jpg
